@PostMapping("/upload")
public Result<String> upload(@RequestParam("file") MultipartFile file) {
    // ❌ 错误：全部读入内存
    byte[] bytes = file.getBytes();

    // ✅ 正确：流式写入
    Path target = Paths.get("/data/uploads/" + file.getOriginalFilename());
    try (InputStream in = file.getInputStream()) {
        Files.copy(in, target, StandardCopyOption.REPLACE_EXISTING);
    }
    return Result.ok("上传成功");
}
```

**分片上传（>500MB）**：

```java
@PostMapping("/chunk")
public Result<String> uploadChunk(
    @RequestParam int chunk,     // 当前片号
    @RequestParam int chunks,    // 总片数
    @RequestParam String md5,    // 文件 MD5
    @RequestParam MultipartFile file
) {
    Path chunkPath = Paths.get("/tmp/chunks/" + md5 + "/" + chunk);
    Files.createDirectories(chunkPath.getParent());
    file.transferTo(chunkPath);

    if (chunk == chunks - 1) {
        // 最后一片，合并
        mergeChunks(md5, chunks);
        return Result.ok("上传完成");
    }
    return Result.ok("分片 " + chunk + " 上传成功");
}

private void mergeChunks(String md5, int chunks) throws IOException {
    Path target = Paths.get("/data/uploads/" + md5);
    try (OutputStream out = Files.newOutputStream(target)) {
        for (int i = 0; i < chunks; i++) {
            Path chunk = Paths.get("/tmp/chunks/" + md5 + "/" + i);
            Files.copy(chunk, out);
            Files.delete(chunk);
        }
    }
}
```

关键：永远用流式读写，别 `getBytes()` 一把梭。

