| 问题 | 场景 | 原因 | 解决方案 |
|------|------|------|----------|
| **缓存穿透** | 查不存在的数据 | 缓存和 DB 都没有，直接打穿到 DB | 布隆过滤器 + 缓存空值 |
| **缓存击穿** | 热点 Key 过期 | 大量并发同时查同一个过期 Key | 互斥锁 / 永不过期 |
| **缓存雪崩** | 大量 Key 同时过期 | 缓存层大面积失效 | 过期时间加随机 / 多级缓存 |

```java
// 1. 缓存穿透：缓存空值
public User getById(Long id) {
    String key = "user:" + id;
    User user = (User) redis.get(key);
    if (user != null) return user;

    // 空值标记
    if (redis.exists(key + ":null")) return null;

    user = db.findById(id);
    if (user == null) {
        redis.setex(key + ":null", 60, "1");  // 空值缓存 1 分钟
        return null;
    }
    redis.setex(key, 3600, user);
    return user;
}

// 2. 缓存击穿：互斥锁
public User getByIdLock(Long id) {
    String key = "user:" + id;
    User user = (User) redis.get(key);
    if (user != null) return user;

    String lockKey = "lock:user:" + id;
    if (redis.setnx(lockKey, "1", 10)) {  // 抢锁
        try {
            user = db.findById(id);
            redis.setex(key, 3600, user);
            return user;
        } finally {
            redis.del(lockKey);
        }
    } else {
        Thread.sleep(100);  // 等一等，再查缓存
        return getByIdLock(id);
    }
}

// 3. 缓存雪崩：过期时间加随机
redis.setex(key, 3600 + new Random().nextInt(600), value);  // ±10 分钟
```

```java
public class ProducerConsumer {
    private final BlockingQueue<String> queue = new LinkedBlockingQueue<>(100);
    private volatile boolean running = true;

    public void start() {
        // 生产者
        new Thread(() -> {
            int i = 0;
            while (running) {
                try {
                    String task = "Task-" + (++i);
                    queue.put(task);  // 队列满时阻塞
                    System.out.println("生产: " + task);
                    Thread.sleep(100);
                } catch (InterruptedException e) {
                    Thread.currentThread().interrupt();
                    break;
                }
            }
        }, "producer").start();

        // 消费者（多线程）
        for (int n = 0; n < 3; n++) {
            new Thread(() -> {
                while (running) {
                    try {
                        String task = queue.poll(2, TimeUnit.SECONDS);
                        if (task == null) continue;
                        System.out.println(Thread.currentThread().getName() + " 消费: " + task);
                        Thread.sleep(300);  // 模拟处理
                    } catch (InterruptedException e) {
                        Thread.currentThread().interrupt();
                        break;
                    }
                }
            }, "consumer-" + n).start();
        }
    }

    public void stop() {
        running = false;
    }
}

// Java 8+ 更优雅：用 CompletableFuture + 线程池
Executor producer = Executors.newSingleThreadExecutor();
ExecutorService consumers = Executors.newFixedThreadPool(3);
// ...
```
关键：`put()` 阻塞插入防 OOM，`poll(timeout)` 阻塞取出允许优雅退出。

```java
@Service
public class ShortUrlService {
    private static final String BASE62 = "0123456789ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz";
    private static final String DOMAIN = "https://s.cn/";

    @Autowired
    private JdbcTemplate jdbc;

    public String shorten(String longUrl) {
        // 1. 先查是否存在
        String exist = jdbc.queryForObject(
            "SELECT short_code FROM short_url WHERE long_url = ?", 
            String.class, longUrl
        );
        if (exist != null) return DOMAIN + exist;

        // 2. 插入记录，用自增 ID 生成短码
        jdbc.update("INSERT INTO short_url (long_url) VALUES (?)", longUrl);
        Long id = jdbc.queryForObject("SELECT LAST_INSERT_ID()", Long.class);

        // 3. ID → Base62
        String code = toBase62(id);
        jdbc.update("UPDATE short_url SET short_code = ? WHERE id = ?", code, id);
        return DOMAIN + code;
    }

    public String redirect(String code) {
        return jdbc.queryForObject(
            "SELECT long_url FROM short_url WHERE short_code = ?",
            String.class, code
        );
    }

    private String toBase62(long num) {
        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
        while (num > 0) {
            sb.append(BASE62.charAt((int)(num % 62)));
            num /= 62;
        }
        return sb.reverse().toString();
    }
}
